Exploring Voting Tendencies

Delia Corridon

Introduction

This project explores how voting tendencies vary across different races, political parties, levels of education, and income brackets through survey data from September 2020. The survey was conducted by Ipsos for FiveThirtyEight. Ipsos surveyed a sample population specifically recruited and curated to be representative of the U.S. population at large.
